name: MathWallet
description: MathWallet is the Multichain Wallet for Web3 that enables token storage of over one hundred chains including BTC, ETH, Polkadot, Cosmos, Filecoin, Solana, BNBChain, etc, supports cross-chain token bridges and multi-chain dApp store. Our investors include Fenbushi Capital, Binance Labs, Fundamental Labs, Multicoin Capital, NGC Ventures, Amber Group, 6Eagle Capital. Visit mathwallet.org for more information.
